Why i am getting high cpc?

High CPC (Cost Per Click) can be influenced by several factors such as your targeting settings, competition in your ad category, and the quality of your ad creative. To address this, you might want to review and adjust your targeting options, improve the relevance and quality of your ad content, or consider testing different bidding strategies. For more detailed guidance on optimizing your campaigns, you can refer to our Reporting Guide here: [Reporting Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18088532505485-Reporting-Guide).
